  "difficultyLevel": 6,
  "lyrics": "You're slipping, you're slipping away, leaving a spot, slipping, and I'll find a way, I won't I'm still lost in this phase, won't be the same, I love you Even if I lost youjstill gonna miss you And all the nights with everything you do Just so lost without you So go ahead and leave, you better believe I'll always be around if you need me Don't disregret, you get what you get, you're the type baby I'll never forget Now I know you're gone, for we stayed so long Just want one more night with everything you do Just so lost without you So kiss me as you leave, I'll always believe Love comes around again, just wait and see Don't disregret, you get what you get, you're the type baby I'll never forget Now I know you're gone, for we stayed so long ",
  "lyricsSegments": [
    {
      "end": 21.600000381469727,
      "text": "You're slipping, you're slipping away, leaving a spot, slipping, and I'll find a way, I won't",
      "start": 2.259999990463257
    },
    {
      "end": 30.360000610351562,
      "text": "I'm still lost in this phase, won't be the same, I love you",
      "start": 21.600000381469727
    },
    {
      "end": 47.15999984741211,
      "text": "Even if I lost youjstill gonna miss you",
      "start": 33.08000183105469
    },
    {
      "end": 53.720001220703125,
      "text": "And all the nights with everything you do",
      "start": 47.880001068115234
    },
    {
      "end": 60.86000061035156,
      "text": "Just so lost without you",
      "start": 55.31999969482422
    },
    {
      "end": 75.12000274658203,
      "text": "So go ahead and leave, you better believe",
      "start": 68.04000091552734
    },
    {
      "end": 85.4800033569336,
      "text": "I'll always be around if you need me",
      "start": 77.87999725341797
    },
    {
      "end": 108.26000213623047,
      "text": "Don't disregret, you get what you get, you're the type baby I'll never forget",
      "start": 99.54000091552734
    },
    {
      "end": 125.37999725341797,
      "text": "Now I know you're gone, for we stayed so long",
      "start": 111.86000061035156
    },
    {
      "end": 131.9600067138672,
      "text": "Just want one more night with everything you do",
      "start": 125.37999725341797
    },
    {
      "end": 139.60000610351562,
      "text": "Just so lost without you",
      "start": 131.9600067138672
    },
    {
      "end": 154.1999969482422,
      "text": "So kiss me as you leave, I'll always believe",
      "start": 148.60000610351562
    },
    {
      "end": 161.94000244140625,
      "text": "Love comes around again, just wait and see",
      "start": 155.89999389648438
    },
    {
      "end": 186.9199981689453,
      "text": "Don't disregret, you get what you get, you're the type baby I'll never forget",
      "start": 178.02000427246094
    },
    {
      "end": 213.02000427246094,
      "text": "Now I know you're gone, for we stayed so long",
      "start": 211.6199951171875
